reviewText: This is one of my projects and it's good if you don't compare it to a major production. It is amateur class and for that I think it's decent. It's electronic rock meets progressive guitarist.  Both musicians sing and it was done long distance. !0 songs and 10 Videos,  The music is better than the videos and can be had independently here on Amazon https://amzn.com/B00GSA7162

It's so good to see independent artist that have some imagination and are not just trying to sound like eveyone else. Though half the music is instrumental it still gives you a foundation to create your own interpetations that fit with the concepts of the lyrical stories. Very well done videos and music!

Well worth a few bucks!
